{"tid":2421251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登將簽行政命令加強晶片等產品供應鏈　減依賴中國","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T00:48:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe73023cac598323d02ab661b4038a50c91e585","tid":2421251,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"拜登將簽行政命令加強晶片等產品供應鏈　減依賴中國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425126&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8ANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=03eb0163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425126&h=d729f636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425126</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中美科技戰引發晶片荒，有報道指，美國總統拜登將簽署行政命令，強化科技戰略產品的供應鏈，尋求與台灣、南韓等合作，減少對中國的依賴。國會亦正計劃草擬法案，加強應對中國崛起。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n美國總統拜登邀請部分國會共和民主兩黨議員，星期三到白宮討論全球晶片荒對美國科技產業的影響，預料拜登將簽署行政命令，加強微晶片等重要產品的供應鏈。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《日本經濟新聞》報道，行政命令指示發展國家供應鏈策略，強化供應網絡應對災難或制裁的影響，集中於半導體、車用電池、稀土和醫療產品，加強與台灣、南韓、日本、澳洲等合作，減少對中國的依賴，美國可能建議合作夥伴減少跟中國做生意。<br />\n<br />\n參議院多數黨領袖舒默亦已要求兩黨議員草擬法案，加強美國的競爭力，應對中國崛起。<br />\n<br />\n舒默：「新法案必須達成三個目標：增加美國應對中國的競爭力；透過美國創新、勞工及生產力，投資於戰略性夥伴及盟友北約、東南亞和印度；曝露、遏制及一次過終結中國損害無數美國職位的掠奪行為。」<br />\n<br />\n舒默期望參議院在春天前審議有關法案，他指，目前半導體產業是美國經濟及國家安全的危險弱點，這種情況必須改變。<br />\n<br />\n路透社獨家報道，兩黨參議員最快周三提案，對抗中國審查美國企業，倡議設立工作組監控及應對中國對美國人和美國企業的審查和威脅，例如向電影業、航空業界等施壓。"},{"pid":"5b693fd79ad80abe4b585866d4f4bb687419fa8b","tid":2421251,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"登fans開始自hi"},{"pid":"574b2eb8a66ea9150168e110a49d67c7d54caf77","tid":2421251,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"低端晶片先係中國製，高端全部台灣製<br />\n<br />\n定係republic of china is China?"},{"pid":"fc0eab3ad0a3083aa61510d26e9075de354a3a31","tid":2421251,"uid":109780,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ei0hep.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ei0hep.gif&h=fc6cf565&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4727c8d0bdd710dd67d9bbdb6c3beb992b0e6686","tid":2421251,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:43:39.000Z","msg":"愛侵力：我睇唔到 你左膠 泛民 PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0570f76b850628a5c7b70a023906ec9d07076736","tid":2421251,"uid":25825,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc0eab3ad0a3083aa61510d26e9075de354a3a31","tid":2421251,"uid":109780,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ei0hep.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ei0hep.gif&h=fc6cf565&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"Action 斬首左淋病未？<br />\n<br />\nChina Joe 任內出現 Myanmar 政變<br />\n唔記得咗<br />\nChina Trump 任內出現白羅斯 泰國 示威？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7120fd6ee7ac688879a25404e012a850a98d605d","tid":2421251,"uid":221530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"我唔反登了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599d3c5ef54bd741efb9b9e1d9201c547d7a8e97","tid":2421251,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"簽撚左過百份行政命令未"},{"pid":"67089502a5c3c6776fde9392d5c6eebe773cb6e8","tid":2421251,"uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"574b2eb8a66ea9150168e110a49d67c7d54caf77","tid":2421251,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"低端晶片先係中國製，高端全部台灣製<br />\n<br />\